      \xi)}{\phi(v)}\right)^2+\left(\frac{\eta}{\phi(v)}\right)^2+\left(\frac{\zeta}{\phi(v)}\right)^2&=c^2\left(\frac{\beta(\frac{v\xi}{c^2}+\tau)}{\phi(v)}\right)^2\\
  \frac{\beta^2(v\tau +
